Do you need a new single bath vanity at an affordable price that will fit into a small bathroom? Then look no further than this 72 in. Double bath vanity set from. It's stylish, priced to fit any budget. (2 display 24 in. by 36 in silver mirror with matching wooden frame may be available in the showroom) There is a Carrera marble top, and a porcelain undermount sink. This vanity is crafted from solid wood and features dovetail jointed drawers for long-lasting durability. This product is not available for shipping and must be picked up at our Phoenix location.

• Dovetail drawer joints.
• DTC Fully-extending under-mount soft close
• drawer slides and hinge.
• Dimensions - 72.00 x 22.00 x 36.00 in

Includes:
• White Carrera marble or Quartz top
• CUPC under mount porcelain sinks.
*Faucet sold separately
